{"tid":665222,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"孫悟空的小故事","createTime":"2018-05-14T17:58:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-14T19:12:34.000Z","uid":186665,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"742061166dd15e70dfd1aa6b242c15011c8c41df","tid":665222,"uid":186665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T17:58:52.000Z","msg":"有一日 如來佛祖<br />\n請悟空去仙桃園食桃<br />\n但只可以選一粒最甜既拎走<br />\n悟空去到桃園，好大，有好多桃<br />\n悟空決定每個都咬一啖<br />\n但佢吃左三日三夜，都未食遍個桃園<br />\n佢飽得好辛苦，頂唔順就求其簡左個比佛祖<br />\n拿，呢個最甜啦，我拎呢個走<br />\n你個仆街玩鳩我，我呢世都唔想再食桃<br />\n最後悟空從未試過好好地把一個桃食得乾淨<br />\n佛說:痛苦嗎<br />\n悟空:屌你啦，攞景定贈慶啊<br />\n佛說:如果比你簡多次，你一開始就拎走一個<br />\n相信佢就係最甜既你會開心點嗎<br />\n悟空恍然大悟，其實佢早就唔記得食過咁多個，到底邊個係甜啲啦<br />\n開心 是選擇<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n女朋友會否明白我講既呢個故事"},{"pid":"1de0d6d43e52c3239b1ede96044a16117f85b0e0","tid":665222,"uid":186665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T18:01:04.000Z","msg":"有冇人睇，文筆麻麻，寫得唔好"},{"pid":"19b7af078df309bfc580fe6306ba05907d12f7f2","tid":665222,"uid":118381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T18:03:11.000Z","msg":"幾有趣，支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82fedfb1deba1467a2a9da7d2fb89083473c613a","tid":665222,"uid":30829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T18:04:28.000Z","msg":"個意思幾好"},{"pid":"d756f8f4cd570bb727e75f988dca95622a40b6d5","tid":665222,"uid":86819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T18:04:46.000Z","msg":"Le度咁多小學生<br />\n邊睇得明你寫乜9丫"},{"pid":"2b3e17c9d757e5bd2f858eb6f7b69e0a6e6137f5","tid":665222,"uid":186665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d756f8f4cd570bb727e75f988dca95622a40b6d5","tid":665222,"uid":86819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T18:04:46.000Z","msg":"Le度咁多小學生<br />\n邊睇得明你寫乜9丫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T18:08:12.000Z","msg":"咁又係，小學生一定會話<br />\n個桃園咁大，咁多桃，你唔係試都唔試<br />\n就拎一個走話最甜啊麻，咁浪費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84d5aeb2691624187462e8555b05adf25eda9034","tid":665222,"uid":181221,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T18:34:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c3b9004e3556b74b2ddadf9693af5929bd549818","tid":665222,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T18:39:34.000Z","msg":"簡單易明"},{"pid":"ee467e0a50de3531f448d89054d3083196eb6ef9","tid":665222,"uid":186665,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"84d5aeb2691624187462e8555b05adf25eda9034","tid":665222,"uid":181221,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T18:34:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T19:10:46.000Z","msg":"我都冇話係我作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都係聽返黎咁上下，寫出黎都要大家睇得明架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可唔可以分享下柏拉圖個故事比我"},{"pid":"cadcc920ab772185f71b9e40dabb6e6561cc055e","tid":665222,"uid":181221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T19:12:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}